<h1>Write your own text here</h1>
<h2>You can use different title sizes</h2>
The system for editing text is simple: it just allows you to use different markups such as:
<ul>
<li>Lists, of course</li>
<li><a href="www.google.com">Hypertext links (click me!)</a></li>
<li>Images</li>
<li><b>Bold</b> and <i>Italic</i></li>
<li>...</li>
</ul>





